quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify;\">Call of Juarez: Gunslinger</em><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;noto sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;apple color emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;kisahkan Silas Greaves, seorang pemburu bayaran abad 19 yang tengah memburu Roscoe “Rustling Bob” Bryant. Seri ini adalah yang paling underrated yang pernah ada di masanya dengan gunfight yang apik dan eksplorasi yang menarik. Kali ini, gamenya gratis di Steam.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;noto sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;apple color emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Benar sekali, Techland gratiskan&nbsp;</span><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;noto sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;apple color emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify;\">Call of Juarez: Gunslinger</em><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;noto sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;apple color emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;permanen di Steam. Kamu hanya bisa mendapatkan gamenya hingga tanggal 15 Desember 2021 jam 01:00 WIB.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;noto sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;apple color emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Kamu yang telah mengklaimnya bisa memiliki gamenya selamanya di library Steam milikmu tanpa perlu khawatir gamenya akan ditarik. Tunggu apalagi? Buruan klaim.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;noto sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;apple color emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;noto sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;apple color emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;noto sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;apple color emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui emoji&quot;, &quot;segoe ui symbol&quot;, &quot;noto color emoji&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></span><br></p>', '2021-12-14 16:55:00', '2021-12-29 06:57:00', 1, 'Call-of-Juarez:-Gunslinger-Gratis-Permanen-dalam-Waktu-Terbatas-di-PC', '67504ae7b87bf9e9ee80d094e8bcaac4.jpg', 15, 'KarinaA', NULL);
